<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_232" id="115v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_232_r2l10"><expan>VVılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Sawnſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> Vogt cʒü Spekfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_232_r2l11"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> vvılhalm / Als Jr vns vormals vnd auch <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l12">habt / von Heincʒen Sprengen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / wiſſen wir cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit keinen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l13">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den das antreff / . Dann als Jr begert / vvöllen wir Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l14">durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen vnſer geleitte <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ er das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l15">vier tag / wenn er <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd mitvaſten / cʒü vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vvıl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l16"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd kümt er in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit cʒü vns / So wöllen wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l17">ſein rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> hören / . vnd wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew auch vormals ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">geſch </del> an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brıefe <expan>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſen / . vnd ıſt <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> brief <expan>ſıd<ex>er</ex></expan> alſo beſıgelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l19">da <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ des <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l20">vvo wir ew lıeb vnd <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r2l21">allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Jnuocauit / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_232" id="115v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Sawnsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>, vogt czü Spekfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Wilhalm, als ir uns vormals und auch
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Heinczen Sprengen
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, wissen wir czü
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit keinen der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, den das antreff. Dann, als ir begert,
                        wöllen wir im durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen unser geleitte
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sol
                        vier tag, wenn er <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und mitvasten czü uns
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und kümt er in
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit czü uns, so wöllen wir sein rede
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> hören. Und wir
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew auch vormals ein
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> briefe
                                <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen, und ist
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> brief <expan>sid<ex>er</ex></expan> also
                        besigelt da <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz des
                            <expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gevord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hat. Und wo wir ew lieb und
                                <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> invocavit.</ab>
</div>
